TI  - The new social landscape: Relationships among social media use, social skills, and offline friendships from age 10–18 years
AU  - Steinsbekk, Silje
AU  - Bjørklund, Oda
AU  - Valkenburg, Patti
AU  - Nesi, Jacqueline
AU  - Wichstrøm, Lars
